text: Vilhelm Hellman (7 December 1922 - 7 November 1991) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Örnsköldsvik Municipality
